---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: false
bodyClass: home
---
<section class="hero wrap">
  <p class="eyebrow">Ziyan Song · Software Engineer</p>
  <h1 class="hero__title">
    I build AI products.<br />
    I write <em>to think.</em>
  </h1>
  <p class="hero__lede">
    I'm a software engineer building AI-native products, agent systems, and full-stack
    applications. I enjoy turning early ideas into usable products quickly — shaping
    product flows, building the systems behind them, and improving them through fast
    iteration. I care about clean architecture, reliable infrastructure, and thoughtful
    product details.
  </p>
  <div class="hero__actions">
    <a class="btn btn--primary" href="/projects/">See my work</a>
    <a class="btn btn--ghost" href="/about/">About me</a>
  </div>
  <p class="hero__epigraph">
    The great world lies ahead, and the lucky ones among us are given the chance to
    explore it.
  </p>
</section>

<section class="home-section wrap">
  <div class="section-head">
    <h2 class="section-head__title">Selected Projects</h2>
    <a class="section-head__more" href="/projects/">All projects →</a>
  </div>
  {% include "partials/project-index.njk" %}
</section>

<section class="home-section wrap">
  <div class="home-split">
    <div class="home-split__col">
      <div class="section-head">
        <h2 class="section-head__title">Technical Notes</h2>
        <a class="section-head__more" href="/technical-notes/">All →</a>
      </div>
      <ul class="mini-list">
        {% for note in collections.notes | limit(4) %}
          <li>
            <a href="{{ note.url }}">
              <span class="mini-list__title">{{ note | preferredNoteTitle(collections.noteTranslation) }}</span>
              <time class="mini-list__date" datetime="{{ note.date | isoDate }}">{{ note.date | readableDate }}</time>
            </a>
          </li>
        {% endfor %}
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="home-split__col">
      <div class="section-head">
        <h2 class="section-head__title">From the Notebook</h2>
        <a class="section-head__more" href="/notes-essays/">All →</a>
      </div>
      <ul class="mini-list mini-list--serif">
        {% for w in collections.writing | limit(5) %}
          <li>
            <a href="{{ w.url }}">
              <span class="mini-list__title">{{ w.data.title or (w.date | readableDate(w.data.lang)) }}</span>
              <time class="mini-list__date" datetime="{{ w.date | isoDate }}">{{ w.date | readableDate(w.data.lang) }}</time>
            </a>
          </li>
        {% endfor %}
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
